#KMS keys
- CMK keys cannot be deleted Immeditly ,It takes 7 days after marrking it for deletion.
- KMS keys dont rotate by default.
    - During the rotation new data will be encryted with new CMK and older data wil decrypted by previous save backing day.
    
    
    
    
